<H3> <TI>   Assembly Official Says Session To Open 26 May </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Assembly Official Says Session To Open 26 May </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK2005115194 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network in Vietnamese 
1100 GMT 20 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK2005115194 </F>
<F P=104>  Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network </F>
<F P=105>  Vietnamese </F>


