<F P=100> North Korea </F>
<H3> <TI>   Article by Russian Paper Praises Kim Chong-il </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Article by Russian Paper Praises Kim Chong-il </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK2105113994 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1052 GMT 21 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK2105113994 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> ["`Important Lesson From Struggle for the Cause of </F>
Socialism'" -- KCNA headline] 
  [Text] Pyongyang, May 21 (KCNA) -- Papers here Friday 
carried "Important Lesson From Struggle for the Cause of 
Socialism", an article by Mikhail Zemskov, chief editor of the 
Russian paper PATRIOT. 
  In the article the author wrote that the reality in which 
socialism has suffered a setback and capitalism revived in some 
countries in recent years gave the serious lesson that of 
paramount importance in smashing challenges of the imperialist 
allied forces and steadily advancing the cause of socialism is 
to correctly solve the question of succeeding to the 
revolutionary cause, the question of succeeding to leadership. 
  Stating that he has read many famous works of Comrade Kim 
Chong- il including "The Historical Lesson in Building Socialism 
and the General Line of Our Party", "On the Fundamentals of 
Revolutionary Party Building" and "Abuses of Socialism Are 
Intolerable" and visited Korea on several occasions and made a 
deep analysis of the reality, he said he deeply realized in this 
course that the question of succeeding to leadership is not only 
the basic factor of the advance of the socialist cause in Korea 
but the main point decisive of the rise or fall of the 
international communist movement. 
  The socialist cause, the revolutionary cause of chuche which 
was started and has been developed by Comrade Kim Il-song is 
being successfully carried forward by the heir to him, Comrade 
Kim Chong-il, to accomplishment, the author wrote, and went on: 
  Characteristic of the leadership of Comrade Kim Chong-il for 
carrying forward the cause of socialism to accomplishment is 
that he is accelerating the cause of socialism at faster pace 
not only by defending and succeeding to the outstanding 
ideological and theoretical activities and immortal exploits of 
Comrade Kim Il-song but also by developing and enriching them in 
conformity with the requirements of the development of the times 
and with the aspirations of the people. 
  In carrying forward the cause of socialism, the 
revolutionary 
cause of chuche, to accomplishment Comrade Kim Chong-il has 
effected new innovations in the revolution and construction as a 
whole, always set bold goals and attained them successfully. As 
a result, fundamental changes have taken place in all fields 
including the party and state affairs, economic and cultural 
construction and the building of revolutionary Armed Forces. 
  The expansion in scope and development of the cause of 
socialism, the revolutionary cause of chuche pioneered by 
Comrade Kim Il-song in the Democratic People's Republic of 
Korea, fully show the great personality of Comrade Kim Chong-il 
as an outstanding and tested leader. 
  What I must stress in particular among the victories and 
successes made by Comrade Kim Chong-il in carrying forward and 
developing the cause of socialism is the singlehearted unity of 
the leader, the party and the masses. 
  In Korea today the whole party, the entire Army and all the 
people are unfailingly loyal to their leader, devotedly 
upholding his cause and firmly united ideologically and 
purposefully and In- moral obligations. 
  All the people regard Comrade Kim Chong-il, an illustrious 
leader, as their father and are united behind him in one mind. 
Herein lie the source of the invincibility and durability of the 
Korean-style socialism. 
  The Democratic People's Republic of Korea (DPRK) is 
shattering to pieces the anti-DPRK, anti-socialist moves of the 
imperialists, defending the security of the country and the 
dignity of the nation and safeguarding and developing the 
socialist system with its invincible revolutionary Armed Forces 
and with the might of singlehearted unity. 
  Conclusions drawn from the present realities of the DPRK, 
now 
a socialist bastion, and of the international communist movement 
which is undergoing ordeals in face of all challenges bespeak 
that the cause of socialism will be firmly defended and 
accomplished if leadership over the revolution and construction 
is carried forward by an outstanding leader, but, otherwise it 
will play into the hands of the renegades of socialism and end 
in failure. 
  The DPRK where the question of succeeding to leadership has 
been solved successfully by Comrade Kim Chong-il, a genuine 
people's leader, serves as a model of world socialism, as a 
beacon of hope for the people who are fighting for socialism and 
communism. 
  Political and public figures and progressive people of many 
countries in the world look up to and revere Comrade Kim 
Chong-il, the dear leader of the Korean people, as the 
outstanding leader of the present times and are rising in the 
struggle to defend and develop the cause of socialism. 
  Socialism, the ideal and aspiration of mankind, is sure to 
be 
crowned with victory. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

