west-northwest, it said. 
  Maritime Safety Agency officials suspect the passengers may 
be attempting to enter Japan illegally, TBS said. 
  On Wednesday, a group of 138 Chinese were apprehended while 
hiding in a warehouse at Hakata port in Fukuoka. They were 
arrested for allegedly entering the country illegally. 

