<H4>    `Psychological Boost' Expected </H4>

<F P=102> OW2305114894 Tokyo KYODO in English 1107 GMT 23 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW2305114894 </F>
<F P=104>  Tokyo KYODO </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


