<H3> <TI>   Another Lighthouse Being Built on Spratlys </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Another Lighthouse Being Built on Spratlys </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK2005162994 Hanoi VNA in English 1403 GMT 20 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> BK2005162994 </F>
<F P=104>  Hanoi VNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Hanoi VNA May 20 -- A light house is being built on 
the Da Tay Island of Truong Sa Archipelagoes (Spratly) by the 
Maritime Navigation company. 
  When completed, this light house 20 metres in height, will 
be 
visible from 16 nautical miles. 
  Due to difficult working conditions on offshore islands, the 
company leadership constantly takes care of the workers' life, 
providing them with enough foods, vegetables and fresh water. 
The company is now managing nearly 30 light houses from 
northern Province of Quang Ninh to the central Province of Quang 
Nam Da Nang and the Truong Sa archipelagoes in the East Sea. 

</TEXT>

